well it's offically been 2 years. just makes me think about all the shit i;ve been through, all i;ve missed out on, and all the aggravation it's caused. sometimes it makes you wonder if it was all worth it. at times it seemed like i;d been sitting in the sidelines watching everyone else live their lives. christ, i don;t want to even think about all the money and hours i put into this. 
any way, thanks to all of you who have stood by me, and pushed me forward when times seemed bleak. sorry i missed out on so much, but it was all worth it in the end. 
please don;t make me do it again.
